<h2 id="2024" style="text-align: left;">2024 Holiday Deals</h2>
<p>Explore our 2024 holidays for unforgettable walking adventures across Europe.</p>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/21988198ef4c48fd91b8a3e0ce5c119a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/21988198ef4c48fd91b8a3e0ce5c119a}" title="Madeira">Madeira Holidays</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13102401/madeira-são-jorge_adobestock_591761991.jpeg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/73febe22bfd446c7b471769be03fd0dd" /></p>
<p>Discover the beautiful island of Madeira on an Inghams walking holiday. Enjoy spectacular scenery, ocean views, plenty of activities and endless walking trails in the resorts of Canico and Funchal.</p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/21988198ef4c48fd91b8a3e0ce5c119a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/21988198ef4c48fd91b8a3e0ce5c119a}" title="Madeira" class="c-btn">View Madeira Deals</a><br /><a data-udi="umb://document/21988198ef4c48fd91b8a3e0ce5c119a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/21988198ef4c48fd91b8a3e0ce5c119a}" title="Madeira"></a></div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/6513a747ea8a46b899cfd4357ca2743b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6513a747ea8a46b899cfd4357ca2743b}" title="Italy">Italy Holidays</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13102402/italy.jpeg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/652cc449dd9a45d1a1b46d45e5404a0e" /></p>
<p>Discover some of Italy's most scenic destinations with Inghams. From the stunning mountain ranges and lakes in the north to the dramatic cliff side towns on the coast.</p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/6513a747ea8a46b899cfd4357ca2743b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6513a747ea8a46b899cfd4357ca2743b}" title="Italy">View Italy Deals</a></div>
