<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/e7e1e0da7bdb46efb283e1b73cd888cf" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e7e1e0da7bdb46efb283e1b73cd888cf}" title="Austria">Austria Holidays</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13102403/austria.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/1e0fee86b4704bad93e9243518ea8fe1" /></p>
<p>Holidays in Austria continue to charm with their unique combination of fairytale features and local traditions, coupled with hearty cuisine, pretty alpine villages and old fashioned folklore.</p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/e7e1e0da7bdb46efb283e1b73cd888cf" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e7e1e0da7bdb46efb283e1b73cd888cf}" title="Austria" class="c-btn">View Austria Deals</a></div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/a3c4877767844f3d89ad8e5165020482" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a3c4877767844f3d89ad8e5165020482}" title="Slovenia">Slovenia Holidays </a><img src="/media/13102404/slovenia_adobe-stock_330429263_lake-bled.png" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/06ff157b43354c158fd98c3efda2738a" /></h3>
<p>Slovenia holidays take you to the foot of the stunning peaks of the Julian Alps, which is brimming with natural beauty from the deep blue waters of the glorious lakes, deep forests and crystal clear springs.</p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/a3c4877767844f3d89ad8e5165020482" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a3c4877767844f3d89ad8e5165020482}" title="Slovenia" class="c-btn">View Slovenia Deals</a></div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/02a5945a51fe4587bf5aa72b66298bea" href="/{localLink:umb://document/02a5945a51fe4587bf5aa72b66298bea}" title="Switzerland">Switzerland Holidays</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13102405/switzerland-1.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/aa7d7c3ad3e24a8b92742174b4917518" /></p>
<p>Switzerland’s stunning landscape includes dramatic snow-dusted peaks on the mountains of Switzerland, tranquil shimmering lakes, and charming, picturesque towns and villages.</p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/02a5945a51fe4587bf5aa72b66298bea" href="/{localLink:umb://document/02a5945a51fe4587bf5aa72b66298bea}" title="Switzerland" class="c-btn">View Switzerland Deals</a></div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/b04e006ef1604b9e93eb0563af7f0cf8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b04e006ef1604b9e93eb0563af7f0cf8}" title="France">France Holidays</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13102406/france-adobestock_225928576.jpeg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/28942a9f681c43b982492ea788856f08" /></p>
<p>Take a walking holiday in the stunning French Alps and walk underneath the spectacular peaks of Mont Blanc and explore Chamonix, Lake Annecy and Morzine.</p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/b04e006ef1604b9e93eb0563af7f0cf8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b04e006ef1604b9e93eb0563af7f0cf8}" title="France" class="c-btn">View France Deals</a></div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/fdb9db516d8249c4af16bfbedf3294e0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/fdb9db516d8249c4af16bfbedf3294e0}" title="Andorra">Andorra Holidays</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13102408/andorra-adobestock_177057471.jpeg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/7735fa5c78b44d03ada7f5b0c8c2d560" /></p>
<p>Explore one of Europe's smallest countries, with 100 mountains and three natural parks. Enjoy beautiful scenery, delicious mountain flavours and endless walking trails.</p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/fdb9db516d8249c4af16bfbedf3294e0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/fdb9db516d8249c4af16bfbedf3294e0}" title="Andorra" class="c-btn">View Andorra Deals</a></div>
