<p>Experience tranquility and luxury at Gardenhotel Theresia, where lush gardens embrace a heated adventure pool, whirlpool, fountain-filled pond, and a delightful garden restaurant.</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/cd318f0b6b664b1b9e19cfaefeca536e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cd318f0b6b664b1b9e19cfaefeca536e}" title="Gardenhotel Theresia (Hinterglemm)" class="c-btn">View Hotel</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/d9c478a0db7d4deb98f121ee0eed7ab6" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d9c478a0db7d4deb98f121ee0eed7ab6}" title="Hotel Villa Madrina">Hotel Villa Madrina</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13099168/ruda1475-1.jpg" alt="" /></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473}" title="Lake Garda">Lake Garda - Italy</a></p>
