<a data-udi="umb://document/d9c478a0db7d4deb98f121ee0eed7ab6" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d9c478a0db7d4deb98f121ee0eed7ab6}" title="Hotel Villa Madrina" class="c-btn">View Hotel</a></div>
