<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/558cc4ca3c104be7ae1a389c9d7c6610" href="/{localLink:umb://document/558cc4ca3c104be7ae1a389c9d7c6610}" title="Hotel Heliopic">Hotel Heliopic</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 293px; height: 157px;" src="/media/13082466/heliopic-spa.jpg?width=293&amp;height=157&amp;mode=max" alt="Hotel Heliopic" data-udi="umb://media/d4905f845c184dc78c37c12899045de3" /></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/2735e2389f7c411cb3061226ce7548d1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2735e2389f7c411cb3061226ce7548d1}" title="Chamonix">Chamonix - France</a></p>
