<a data-udi="umb://document/558cc4ca3c104be7ae1a389c9d7c6610" href="/{localLink:umb://document/558cc4ca3c104be7ae1a389c9d7c6610}" title="Hotel Heliopic" class="c-btn">View Hotel</a></div>
