<p><a data-udi="umb://document/518cc472770341548f0da194220efeeb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/518cc472770341548f0da194220efeeb}" title="Romantik Hotel Schweizerhof" class="c-btn">View Hotel</a></p>
</div>
