<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/e8f256d55487463f84eb2747682db532" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e8f256d55487463f84eb2747682db532}" title="Hotel Montana">Hotel Montana</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 293px; height: 157px;" src="/media/13096026/hotel-montana-3.jpg?width=293&amp;height=157" alt="Hotel montana" data-udi="umb://media/97651be8d7db49089b30bf4452e9ddfe" /></p>
