<p>Experience the epitome of elegance at this artfully furnished hotel, where you’ll find sweeping lake views, effortless lakeside access via a private elevator - all amidst grand surroundings.</p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/e8f256d55487463f84eb2747682db532" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e8f256d55487463f84eb2747682db532}" title="Hotel Montana" class="c-btn">View Hotel</a></div>
