<p><img style="width: 293px; height: 157px;" src="/media/13096586/wellness-hotel-steiner-293-157.jpg?width=293&amp;height=157" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/54e207cc8a584682ba3b07a92d608ef8" /></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/badef60c48c84cc7bcc52cb12d1f032b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/badef60c48c84cc7bcc52cb12d1f032b}" title="Obertauern">Obertauern - Austria</a></p>
