<a data-udi="umb://document/7ba4e5267289495abe9f0c70e9942a0a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7ba4e5267289495abe9f0c70e9942a0a}" title="Hotel Steiner" class="c-btn">View Hotel</a></div>
