<h2 id="Trending" style="text-align: left;">Trending Resorts for 2024</h2>
<p>Experience an unforgettable holiday in 2024 at these top trending resorts in Europe. Whether you fancy a serene lakeside stroll or an exhilarating mountain hike, these resorts offer the ultimate combination of relaxation, adventure, and awe-inspiring views that will leave you with happy feet and unforgettable memories.</p>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/cad35d37f73d435087041e35025d1da8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cad35d37f73d435087041e35025d1da8}" title="Funchal">Funchal Madeira Holidays 2024</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13098482/adobestock-tropical-garden-madeira-411x252.jpg?width=411&amp;height=252" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/f3631efb583e43ceb789d42ba7a577c5" /></p>
<p><span>Experience the lively city of Funchal with its old town, busy harbour, mountain backdrop and incredible ocean views. </span></p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/cad35d37f73d435087041e35025d1da8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cad35d37f73d435087041e35025d1da8}" title="Funchal" class="c-btn">Find Out More</a></div>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/f6d745a0efdf44b5b28bcd4bee55dbb1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f6d745a0efdf44b5b28bcd4bee55dbb1}" title="Canico">Cani<span>ç</span>o Madeira Holidays 2024</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13098481/botanical-garden_13-1-411x252.jpg?width=411&amp;height=252" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/ba1e5c4b0c534e2cb473c9466b809a5e" /></p>
<p>Caniço is a town set on the coast with beautiful views out towards the ocean. Nature lovers will love its marine life and it's also a great base for walking with easy access by bus to the city of Funchal.</p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/f6d745a0efdf44b5b28bcd4bee55dbb1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f6d745a0efdf44b5b28bcd4bee55dbb1}" title="Canico" class="c-btn">Find Out More</a></div>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/c0a1a2eb5f21493d858ec9013916a8fb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c0a1a2eb5f21493d858ec9013916a8fb}" title="Liguria">Liguria Italy Holidays 2024</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13098463/liguria_portofino_adobestock_209605969411x252.jpg?width=411&amp;height=252" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/813b751a276a402f8aacd0b4235fa3de" /></p>
<p>Come and explore the irresistible charm of Liguria, home to Italy's most breath-taking coastline. Here, you'll find a delightful mix of peaceful villages and trendy seaside towns.</p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/c0a1a2eb5f21493d858ec9013916a8fb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c0a1a2eb5f21493d858ec9013916a8fb}" title="Liguria" class="c-btn">Find Out More</a></div>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/594483304a5f4b47844b444df2c9d975" href="/{localLink:umb://document/594483304a5f4b47844b444df2c9d975}" title="Mayrhofen">Mayrhofen Austria Holidays 2024</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13099179/00000107738_olpererhuette-im-zillertal_olpererhuette_manuel-daum-2.jpg" alt="Mayrhofen holidays" data-udi="umb://media/a9145872b6304d74bdcbd8468e8f1c2f" /></p>
<p>Experience the lively charm of Mayrhofen, a picturesque town known for its vibrant atmosphere, stunning scenery, and endless opportunities for relaxation and adventure.</p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/594483304a5f4b47844b444df2c9d975" href="/{localLink:umb://document/594483304a5f4b47844b444df2c9d975}" title="Mayrhofen" class="c-btn">Find Out More</a></div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/0fe9200934b24cd49d20e1cea080f5da" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0fe9200934b24cd49d20e1cea080f5da}" title="Grindelwald">Grindelwald Switzerland Holidays 2024</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13098478/grindelwald-switzerland-1411x252.jpg?width=411&amp;height=252" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/5e8e28229b144648b840e887b8822d92" /></p>
<p>Explore Grindelwald, a stunning alpine gem nestled beneath the majestic Eiger Mountain, offering picture perfect views and lots of walking trails in the Jungfrau region.</p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/0fe9200934b24cd49d20e1cea080f5da" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0fe9200934b24cd49d20e1cea080f5da}" title="Grindelwald" class="c-btn">Find Out More</a></div>
