<p>Step into a real-life fairytale in Bled, Slovenia, where a medieval cliff-top castle and a picturesque church on the island create a truly magical setting.</p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/e0872feec9b24b8db1b30d83108b172e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e0872feec9b24b8db1b30d83108b172e}" title="Lake Bled" class="c-btn">Find Out More</a></div>
